  "html": "<!-- TODO (EJ): add your voice. Factual stub. The image is the actual Pico-8\n     source; a gameplay GIF would be even better when you can grab one. Draft. -->\n<p class=\"\">A Pico-8 \"video game poem\" about the feeling of riding a motorcycle, with speed-reactive perlin-wave road sway and a music engine that escalates through five patterns as speed climbs, then collapses on a crash. EJ's brother made the sprites and tracker music; Coach Artie, EJ's AI assistant, did most of the coding.</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"The motorcycle.p8 source in the Pico-8 editor — perlin road sway and the speed-driven music-pattern engine\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/motorcycle-pico8/source.png\" alt=\"The motorcycle.p8 source in the Pico-8 editor — perlin road sway and the speed-driven music-pattern engine\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/motorcycle-pico8/source.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/motorcycle-pico8/source.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/motorcycle-pico8/source.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/motorcycle-pico8/source.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"The motorcycle.p8 source in the Pico-8 editor — perlin road sway and the speed-driven music-pattern engine\" width=\"1152\" height=\"636\" style=\"--splay-rot:-0.6deg;\" data-dimensions=\"1152×636\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay aspect-video w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">The motorcycle.p8 source in the Pico-8 editor — perlin road sway and the speed-driven music-pattern engine</figcaption>\n</figure>",
